model_explanation: the prosodic focus in S1 is on “ELLEN,” meaning Sam only gave bananas to Ellen, not to anyone else. S2 says Sam also gave Ellen grapes, which contradicts the idea that the only thing given to Ellen was bananas.

the prosodic focus in S1 is on “TOM,” meaning Sam gave bananas to Tom and no one else. S2 says Tom also received apples, which contradicts the exclusivity of giving Tom only bananas.
